  {
    "hotel_id": "7443033",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/sotetsu-fresa-inn-seoul-myeong-dong/hotel/seoul-kr.html",
    "name": "Sotetsu Fresa Inn Seoul Myeong-dong",
    "detail": "We stayed for 5 nights. You can't beat the location right in the heart of bustling Myeongdong, near both line of Metro, good restaurants and street food, shopping. very safe at night. We had good sleep quality & all the linen were fresh & new. All facilities were functional. Only minor thing is that the Comfort Twin room with extra bed is too tight for 3 Asian adults, so it'll be crazy for big, tall people. So next time we'll definitely stay again but with a higher room type. Note: two elevators are not linked so be sure tap on both calling buttons. check-in and out are self-control so super convenient. The flow: come to hotel, through 2 automatic doors at GF, use elevator to Lobby at 13F, there're self checkin machines, choose the languages, follow the step to scan one Passport of the booker, then how many room cards you want. That's it. Check-out for paid reservation is by clicking one in-room button, so again, quick & convenient.",
